Package: libdrilbo-common
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Provides localization data for libdrilbo.
 This package is required by all packages which are utilizing libdrilbo.

Package: libdrilbo-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: libdrilbo-common,
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: Imaging support library for the fizmo Z-Machine interpreter.
 This library provides imaging functions related to the fizmo interpreter.

